data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Step into this beautiful open-concept home with dark hardwood flooring that spans throughout. The interior offers a spacious split floor plan, allowing for maximum privacy, while the separate dining area adds an cozy touch to your dining experiences. Inside, you'll also find a home that's been well-maintained, with a new HVAC system installed in 2020 and the roof updated in 2019. Beyond the interiors, enjoy the convenience of a 12x18 storage shed with electric, a 2-car carport, and a fenced-in backyard, offering the perfect blend of comfort and functionality.
